{"tid":1289270,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"七月瑞士有冇得滑雪？","createTime":"2019-07-06T04:32:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T20:48:55.000Z","uid":137233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3548e6257927387c31f6cb7642946c04e77fd883","tid":1289270,"uid":137233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:32:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"970d02271ac251730f571182a84989323d23d790","tid":1289270,"uid":81021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T11:06:52.000Z","msg":"認真滑嘅話可以去 Zermatt 滑 summer ski。<br />\n諗住係咁兒滑幾個鐘，又本身計劃上少女峰嘅話就喺嗰度嘅 Snow Fun Park 玩吓。"},{"pid":"8990879317f35ccbae710850ed8d6cbd09847988","tid":1289270,"uid":137233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"970d02271ac251730f571182a84989323d23d790","tid":1289270,"uid":81021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T11:06:52.000Z","msg":"認真滑嘅話可以去 Zermatt 滑 summer ski。<br />\n諗住係咁兒滑幾個鐘，又本身計劃上少女峰嘅話就喺嗰度嘅 Snow Fun Park 玩吓。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T12:22:04.000Z","msg":"未滑過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />身上乜都冇"},{"pid":"2449aed2efde11d42b8db769a4bde83bd63dec5e","tid":1289270,"uid":81021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T12:46:38.000Z","msg":"未滑過就有啲搲頭，我未去過 Zermatt 滑唔知嗰度點環境。<br />\n上年去少女峰個 Snow Fun Park 玩，如果租 Ski 或者 board 嘅話，賣飛嗰位會提你唔識滑嘅話最好唔好租呢啲玩。我估應該係因為嗰度查實唔多人會玩 ski，大部份人都係玩 Tubing  同 Sledging 嗰啲，如果完全唔識控制嘅話，滑落條主雪道嗰陣可能容易同其他玩 Sledging 嗰啲炒埋一碟。<br />\n不過少女峰個 Snow Fun Park 除咗兩條主雪道之外，重有一條十零廿尺長嘅 ski lift，完全唔識諗住體驗吓、著吓啲裝備影吓相嗰隻嘅話都可以喺嗰個位 Hea 吓嘅。基本上如果完全未滑過嘅話上少女峰個 Snow Fun Park 租 ski 同 board 應該要有心理準備唔會真係滑到，只係去影吓相 Hea 吓嗰隻。<br />\n我覺得如果真係想去到認真滑嘅話，一係要預足夠時間喺個雪場揾教練，咁嘅話我估你要預四五日留喺個雪場度玩特訓咁玩。<br />\n唔係嘅話就不如去深圳廣州嗰啲室內雪場練到一定程度先去玩。"},{"pid":"33d070b06d81620ed99edb32ac82b4ce2b542821","tid":1289270,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T12:59:26.000Z","msg":"我覺得未滑過唔好去zermatt<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d81b5724c611cdabaeff3da8b63e8455a9578f2c","tid":1289270,"uid":251510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3548e6257927387c31f6cb7642946c04e77fd883","tid":1289270,"uid":137233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:32:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:56:01.000Z","msg":"應該有<br />\n<br />\n利申：試過七月喺瑞士滑雪"},{"pid":"b8e5c4a5a78290ebab0007b2048674050ed6f20f","tid":1289270,"uid":137233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d81b5724c611cdabaeff3da8b63e8455a9578f2c","tid":1289270,"uid":251510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3548e6257927387c31f6cb7642946c04e77fd883","tid":1289270,"uid":137233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:32:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:56:01.000Z","msg":"應該有<br />\n<br />\n利申：試過七月喺瑞士滑雪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T20:48:55.000Z","msg":"Where?"}]}